data.name: 0000 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: U-um, I was hearing from Kyon earlier.

data.name: 0001 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: About whether or not Nagato resembles a cat…

data.name: 0002 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: He said that you had brought it up when you went to the Computer Society.

data.name: 0003 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Ah, that. Yes yes, Yuki has sort of a cat-like image to her, doesn't she?

data.name: 0004 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You get that sort of impression just by looking at her, don't you think?

data.name: 0005 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Yes… I suppose they feel similar to each other.

data.name: 0007 (278.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: Yuki is like a kitty cat?

data.name: 0008 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Do you get that same feeling, little sister?

data.name: 0009 (278.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: Hmm, I probably don't know…

data.name: 0010 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Then try to picture this…

data.name: 0011 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Yuki wearing a pair of cute cat ears, a collar with a bell on it, and a long tail to top it all off.

data.name: 0012 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Don't you think that would suit her?

data.name: 0013 (278.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: Yep, it would really suit her!

data.name: 0014 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Though personally, I imagine her as a pure white cat.

data.name: 0015 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Surprisingly though, a black cat doesn't feel too bad either. Which camp are you in, Mikuru?

data.name: 0017 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Huh? M-me?

data.name: 0018 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Don't black cats have sort of a mischievous energy to them?

data.name: 0019 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: That feels a bit different from Yuki… And yet, it still seems like it fits somehow.

data.name: 0020 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I-I think either way suits her.

data.name: 0021 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You're right, it's hard to rule out either black or white. Let's set this problem aside for now.

data.name: 0023 (278.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: If Yuki is a cat, then what animal is Mikuru?

data.name: 0024 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Mikuru? Hmm…

data.name: 0025 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Mikuru has to be a bunny. I can't imagine anything else!

data.name: 0027 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I-I'm a bunny?

data.name: 0028 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: The bunny suit was such a perfect match for you—just as I'd anticipated!

data.name: 0029 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Oh yeah, next time I definitely have to get Yuki to wear a cat ear headband.

data.name: 0030 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: They're also selling tight-fitting one-piece catsuits, so…

data.name: 0031 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: If we could get cat cosplay Yuki, and bunny girl Mikuru together…

data.name: 0032 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It'll be a moe overload!

data.name: 0034 (278.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: What about you, Haru-nyan?

data.name: 0035 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Me? Hm… Right.

data.name: 0036 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I have a bunny suit of my own, but I can't just be the same as Mikuru.

data.name: 0037 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: In that case, I've gotta be a wolf, right? I wonder if they sell wolf suits?

data.name: 0039 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: But in the first place, it all depends on whether Nagato will dress up as a cat for you…

data.name: 0040 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: She will.

data.name: 0041 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I mean, Yuki seems like the type who'd just nod quietly and do it.

data.name: 0042 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I-I guess that's true. I get the same feeling.

data.name: 0043 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Yuki wearing a cat outfit is such a good idea. We've seriously got to try it out sometime!

data.name: 0044 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: #P06…Sorry, Nagato.

data.name: 0045 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Did you say something?

data.name: 0046 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: N-no, nothing.

data.name: 0047 (278.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: I wonder what Kyon would be?

data.name: 0048 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Kyon? Isn't it obvious?

data.name: 0049 (278.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: A sloth. There's simply no other option.

data.name: 0051 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: A-ahaha…

data.name: 0052 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I somehow diverted us into a weird tangent, but it looks like it bought us some time.

data.name: 0053 (278.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: I'm rooting for you Kyon. Please do your best.
